✖️POCOLOCO✖️
My kind of brunch, definitely enjoyed everything pocoloco have served us, from nachos to tacos and quesadillas, they really proved us that they are one of the the finest restaurants around @thebeachdubai that serve Mexican food.
•
One good thing about this restaurant is they do not just focus on Mexican food they also offer Latin American - Japanese Fusion cuisine and on my next visit i would definitely wanna try it. ❤
•
Kudos to all the servers here, super friendly and accommodating, they even helped us in doing flatlays 😂😍 hooray!
